headline: 3 Reasons to Sell MTD and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Mettler-Toledo’s 25.7% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 9.4%, and its stock price has climbed to $1,406 per share. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
